data.description: Recently Closed - A Modern New Construction Gem!  This home, just closed 90 days ago, boasts the epitome of living. The kitchen is a chef's dream with sleek stainless steel appliances and elegant quartz countertops. Every room in this house is thoughtfully designed to welcome natural light, creating an inviting and bright interior.  You'll find a host of valuable upgrades, including: Blinds, Air conditioning, Quartz Counter tops  With the inclusion of a den that can potentially become an additional bedroom with its private bath, you have endless possibilities for customization. Plus, enjoy the luxury of the largest lot in the development and a covered patio, perfect for outdoor relaxation and entertainment.
